loop - it means continue iteration count

mainly 3 type of loop 
- while
  syntax : 
    while(condition){
       // statements
    }

- do..while
  do{
    //statements
  }while(condition)

- for
  for(declaration; initialization; increment/decrement )
  {
    //statements
  }

for loop also used in array and object 
